    <h3 itemprop="headline">Split in half from space: satellite images confirm Ukraine's 800km drone strike destroyed an irreplaceable Russian Tu-95 bomber</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Russia painted fake Tu-95s on the tarmac and built 17 shelters to protect the real ones. Ukraine's drones flew 800km and split an actual bomber in half anyway.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/07/22/split-in-half-from-space-satellite-images-confirm-ukraines-800km-drone-strike-destroyed-an-irreplaceable-russian-tu-95-bomber/"  >(Rahim Amir, TechRadar)</a>
