        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The real math crisis isn&#8217;t the test scores. It&#8217;s the test</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      This past school year, Cambridge, Massachusetts, placed every eighth grader in Algebra I. It didn’t go well. Ultimately, more than 60% of rising ninth graders will repeat the course.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/07/23/the-real-math-crisis-isnt-the-test-scores-its-the-test/"  >(Ted Dintersmith, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
