    <h3 itemprop="headline">New poll complicates Vance&#8217;s status as Trump&#8217;s likely 2028 heir apparent</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Marco Rubio surged from 7% to 26% in New Hampshire&apos;s latest GOP primary poll, dramatically closing the gap with JD Vance in the hypothetical 2028 presidential nomination race.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/23/poll-complicates-vance-status-trump-likely-2028-heir-apparent/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
