      <img src="/static15/politics/2026/07/23/lindell-plays-up-trump-endorsement-at-sauk-centre-rally.webp" alt="Trump-endorsed Mike Lindell makes his case to voters" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump-endorsed Mike Lindell makes his case to voters</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Fresh off an endorsement from President Donald Trump, Republican Mike Lindell held a town hall meeting in Sauk Centre where he promised to “make Minnesota great again” if primary voters nominate him next month to run for governor.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/23/lindell-plays-up-trump-endorsement-at-sauk-centre-rally/"  >(Tadeo Ruiz Sandoval, MPR News)</a>
