    <h3 itemprop="headline">Fox News Poll: Voters oppose the Iran war, see prolonged commitment</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A Fox News poll finds 56% oppose U.S. military action against Iran, while Trump&apos;s handling of the conflict hits a record-low 34% approval rating.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/23/fox-news-poll-voters-oppose-iran-war-see-prolonged-commitment/"  >(Fox News)</a>
