    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Andy Burnham becomes U.K. prime minister</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      In a transition of power presided over by King Charles, Andy Burnham has replaced Keir Starmer as the United Kingdom's prime minister. Both are from the center-left Labour Party.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/20/npr-andy-burnham-prime-minister-keir-starmer/"  >(Lauren Frayer, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
