  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 22 Jul 2026 19:04:12 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Cathy Wurzer and Matthew Alvarez, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static15/politics/2026/07/22/mike-lindell-may-hurt-minnesota-gop-candidates-in-november-gop-strategist-says.webp" alt="GOP strategist: Lindell may hurt Minn. GOP in November" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">GOP strategist: Lindell may hurt Minn. GOP in November</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      If MyPillow CEO Mike Lindell prevails in the Aug. 11 primary and becomes the GOP’s candidate for governor, “it will definitely have an impact” on other races, GOP strategist Amy Frederiksen told MPR News.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/22/mike-lindell-may-hurt-minnesota-gop-candidates-in-november-gop-strategist-says/"  >(Cathy Wurzer and Matthew Alvarez, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 23 Jul 2026 20:44:17 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 23 Jul 2026 20:44:17 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static15/politics/2026/07/23/trump-endorsement-fails-clear-gop-field-former-governor-joins-south-carolina-senate-race.webp" alt="Trump endorsement fails to clear GOP field as former governor joins South Carolina Senate race" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump endorsement fails to clear GOP field as former governor joins South Carolina Senate race</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Mark Sanford joined a crowded GOP field challenging Trump-endorsed Darline Graham in South Carolina&apos;s special Senate primary set for Aug. 11.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/07/23/trump-endorsement-fails-clear-gop-field-former-governor-joins-south-carolina-senate-race/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
